Interface MultiPolygon2D<T extends Polygon2D>

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Geometry2D>, Geometry2D, GeometryCollection2D<T>, MultiSurface2D<T>, java.io.Serializable
public interface MultiPolygon2D<T extends Polygon2D>
extends MultiSurface2D<T>

This is a MultiSurface2D which can only hold Polygon2D- objects It does not provide additional functionality to MultiSurface but is implemented for completeness.

See Simple Feature Specification (pdf).
